Super Event provides their clients with a full range of event planning wedding catering and marquee hire services in Sussex.Not only do they have gourmet catering, they also offer full marquee hire services. Whether you're throwing a surprise anniversary party, a corporate event for clients, or a fairy tale wedding, Super Event has everything to plan your event from start to end. Tony Brewin established Super Event initially as a sole catering company. He realised that dealing with multiple vendors for just one event led to issues and finger pointing making him realise that one company managing all aspects of an occasion was easier. Super Event can also help their customers discover the best location for their wedding occasion thanks to a developed business relationship with multiple Sussex sites.   All of the gourmet dishes the company offers are made on site by their own chefs. Simply high quality, locally sourced foods are used to make fresh dishes. Whether you select foods from their gourmet menu or decide to throw a hog roast, you're certain to find something to fit your taste.When Super Event manages your wedding or occasion, they will supply you with all of the food, the servers, the cutlery, the linens and everything else required to pull off a suitable soiree.   In addition to meal catering, Super Event's marquee hire is also noteworthy. From seats, to ornamentation and flooring, Super Event can provide everything necessary for a fully built pop-up venue. Through a marquee hire, any space and be the ideal venue.  Even the Super Event staff members live up to the wedding and event business's quality standards. All staff members are handpicked for their good attitudes, professional nature, and strong work ethic and are subsequently trained according to their position.
